    "title": "Msaidizi Wetu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "msaidizi wetu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kwenye Injili ya Yohana, neno la Kigiriki <em>paraklētos</em> linarejelea Roho Mtakatifu. Neno hili linamaanisha &quot;aliyeitwa kando&quot; na linamuelezea kama &quot;Msaidizi&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">Yohana 14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">16:7</a>). Neno hili pia linapatikana katika maandiko mengine ya Kigiriki, ambapo linarejelea Msaidizi wa kisheria. Huyu ni mtu anayezungumza kwa niaba ya mtu mahakamani na kutoa ushauri wa kisheria.</p><p>&quot;Mshauri&quot; ni tafsiri ya kawaida, lakini maana yake ya kisasa inayohusiana na saikolojia inaweza kupotosha. Maana ya zamani ya kisheria ya wakili anayetoa ushauri ni sahihi zaidi.</p><p>&quot;Mfariji&quot; ni tafsiri nyingine ya kawaida, lakini inaweza pia kupotosha. Maana ya zamani ya Kiingereza ya mtu anayetoa nguvu, au &quot;mhimiza,&quot; inalingana zaidi na wazo la Agano Jipya la <em>paraklētos.</em></p><p>Yesu alielezea Roho kama <em>msaidizi mwingine</em> &quot;Msaidizi&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">Yohana 14:16</a>). Yesu, Msaidizi wa kwanza, alimtuma Roho Mtakatifu kama Msaidizi wa Pili (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1\">1 Yohana 2:1</a>). Kila kazi ya Roho iliyoelezewa katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1-John16:33\">Yohana 14–16</a> ni kazi ambayo Yesu alifanya mahali pengine katika hadithi za injili. Yesu aliahidi kwamba Roho Mtakatifu angekuja kuwatia moyo, kuwaelekeza, na kuwatia nguvu wafuasi wake. Roho angeendeleza uwepo wa Yesu miongoni mwa wanafunzi wake. Ahadi tano kuhusu Roho zinaonyesha kazi mbalimbali ambazo Roho hufanya (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">Yohana 14:16–17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7-John16:8\">16:7–8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:14\">13–14</a>).</p><p>Roho alipatikana kwa wanafunzi wa Yesu baada ya kifo chake (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:39\">Yohana 7:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:22\">20:22</a>). Sasa Roho anaendelea na kazi na uwepo wa Yesu katika maisha ya Wakristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:26\">14:16–26</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:25\">1 Samweli 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:15\">24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:12\">2 Samweli 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:6-1Kgs12:14\">1 Wafalme 12:6–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:32\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 27:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:18-Job16:22\">Ayubu 16:18–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:26\">Isaya 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1-John16:15\">Yohana 14:1–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:19-Gal3:20\">Wagalatia 3:19–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:13\">6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5\">1 Timotheo 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:6\">Waebrania 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:24\">12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1\">1 Yohana 2:1</a></p>",
